subject: asset(icons): rebuild with solid fills and negative space cuts only
body:
Eliminated all stroke-based rendering. Every element is now a solid
filled shape. Details (hair texture, beard contour, glasses lens holes)
are created via negative space cutout shapes filled with background
color. Matches the reference clipart/vector illustration style.
